text: White Wings Hanau is a professional basketball club based in Hanau, Germany.Team profile at Eurobasket.com The team currently plays in the ProA, the second highest professional division in Germany. The team plays its home games at the Main-Kinzig-Halle, which has a capacity of 1,564 people. ==References== ==External links== *Official website (in German) Category:Basketball teams in Germany
